{"tid":449487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 港鐵 Apple 再成最受港人歡迎僱主","createTime":"2017-10-27T08:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T12:47:37.000Z","uid":64694,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9fc983104e1a149b48f584c67a1095be5ebbd588","tid":449487,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"【晴報專訊】甚麼僱主最吸引打工仔？有調查發現，Google、港鐵和Apple等全球知名科技巨頭及本地大型企業，連續第二年成為最受港人歡迎的僱主，本港打工仔選擇僱主時，最看重公司福利、工作生活平衡及職業保障，而不同世代的僱員，選擇僱主時看重的因素也不同。<br />\n<br />\n每個打工仔都想找到一個好僱主，據jobsDB發表的《2017年十大企業調查報告》，本港800名受訪者提名出最想加入的企業，首三位是Google、港鐵以及Apple，這些公司亦是連續第二年成為最受香港人歡迎的僱主。上榜的10大僱主還包括facebook、國泰航空、太古集團、新鴻基地產、香港上海滙豐銀行、中華電力以及香港賽馬會。<br />\n<br />\n港打工仔看重工作與生活平衡<br />\n<br />\n調查亦收集了來自香港、新加坡、馬來西亞等地逾2.6萬人的意見，不同地區的受訪者在選擇僱主時所優先考慮的因素大不相同，香港人最看重「公司福利」、「工作生活平衡」及「職業保障」，是亞太區中唯一將「工作與生活平衡」納入三大考慮因素的市場，「僱主屬本地公司」是他們認為最不重要的考慮因素；而新加坡人則把「專業的企業文化」、「和諧的工作關係」和「良好晉升機會」列為優先考慮的因素。<br />\n<br />\n調查亦發現，不同世代在選擇僱主時最重視的因素大相逕庭。jobsDB香港區總經理仇崑石表示︰「隨着年齡和經驗增長，打工仔所重視的事情亦會隨之而變化，僱主在招聘人才時應留意不同世代所重視的因素，並建立相應的人力資源和僱主品牌策略，吸引不同年齡層的求職者。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/google-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5-apple-%E5%86%8D%E6%88%90%E6%9C%80%E5%8F%97%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB-225044307.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fgoogle-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5-apple-%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E%25E5%2583%25B1%25E4%25B8%25BB-225044307.html&d=eUE%2BeL1Xlivs6JdDGUmlLhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=1a44ea07\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/google-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5-apple-%E5%86%8D%E6%88%90%E6%9C%80%E5%8F%97%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB-225044307.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoogle就話啫, apple同狗鐵都係最受歡迎...?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 講出黎都笑死人啦, 狗鐵依家仲要行contract制, 又成日壞車, apple就唔知頂到幾耐, 匯豐同國泰前果排先炒左成班人, 咁都入到十大, 真係笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW, 又係晴報<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a30c86a8f2ae8ba2f855313a56b0f0cf8cfd352","tid":449487,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"邊間唔夠人咪吹邊間囉"},{"pid":"d4101ea5c8b94eb647d13dd74b060135fe0823c5","tid":449487,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T08:33:39.000Z","msg":"組團去做波板糖人 有冇人join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946a2acd5b7bbcfec0c63d78bac950ccd3205c7e","tid":449487,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:04:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>組團去做波板糖人 有冇人join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/27/180401_2c6a43f72e9773cf960aa36ff086a948.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F27%2F180401_2c6a43f72e9773cf960aa36ff086a948.jpg&h=b27b5f7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c7e17b745616fa2d23fd43514ce7e9cda0a0974","tid":449487,"uid":47202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:09:34.000Z","msg":"狗鐵 大部份都係兩年contract....最佳顧主? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb9bf3487d9429c3e1d7eb53a46b6d713f81279","tid":449487,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"冇支那公司？月"},{"pid":"19f89e8bea9e69df5b23bfed16dc28a9a74772ae","tid":449487,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗鐵 大部份都係兩年co